@port = 9001

### Create User
POST http://localhost:{{port}}/user
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "John",
    "lastName": "Doe",
    "email": "john.doe@example.com",
    "postcode": "12345",
    "vehicleRegistration": "ABC123",
    "mobileNumber": "1234567890"
}

